anesthesia.comment: anesthesia protocol: induction with isoflurane (5% for induction, 2% for maintenance); when animal is positioned in scanner: bolus of medetomidine (0.05 mg/kg s.c.), isoflurane switched off after 10 minutes, start continuous infusion of medetomidine (0.1 mg/kg/h s.c.) 5 minutes later; after scans: reversal of anesthesia with atipamezole (0.1 mg/kg s.c.)
